Packy and I, who both live in New York, left the city around 2pm yesterday =
to travel to Philadelphia to celebrate our dad=E2=80=99s birthday. By the t=
ime we sat down together for dinner at 6pm, this edition of the Weekly Dose=
 had completely changed.=20
