, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Boom, t=
he supersonic airline, is doing hard things.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The compa=
ny completed the construction of its new Overture Superfactory, where it wi=
ll build its supersonic airliner. Overture should be capable of traveling a=
t Mach 1.7 (1,122 mph) and carrying 64-80 passengers over a range of 4,250 =
nautical miles. It&#8217;s the new age Concorde. New York to London is 3.5 =
hours. Totally changes the game for transatlantic flight.</p><p style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px =
0;">The new superfactory, located at Piedmont Triad International Airport i=
n Greensboro, North Carolina, is the first supersonic airliner factory in t=
he U.S. With a production capacity of 33 aircraft annually and plans to dou=
ble, it is expected to contribute over $32 billion to the local economy and=
 create 2,400 jobs over the next 20 years.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55=
, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Cannot wait=
 to go Booming across the world.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>(5) </span><str=
